oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Tribute to Patsy Cline - 2012-08-25
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Musical tribute to Patsy Cline - Performers include Jessi Alexander; Mandy Barnett; Striking Matches; Emily West; Band includes Harold Bradley on tic-tac bass; Brad Albin on bass guitar, Jimmy Capps on guitar; Bob Mater on drums; Jeff Taylor on piano. Companion to a Patsy Cline exhibit.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Jessi Alexander; Mandy Barnett; Striking Matches; Emily West
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Hosted by Abi Tapia. Performances include; Walking After Midnight (Emily West); You Belong To Me (Emily West); Lovesick Blues (Emily West); Leaving On Your Mind (Jessi Alexander); In Care Of The Blues (Jessi Alexander); So Wrong (Jessi Alexander); Turn The Card Slowly (Striking Matches); She's Got You (Striking Matches); Let The Teardrops Fall (Striking Matches); Band Introductions; Faded Love (Mandy Barnett); Bill Bailey, Won't You Please Come Home (Mandy Barnett); Crazy (Mandy Barnett); Blue Moon Of Kentucky (Band);
